<h3>POST /api/ragpicker/customers</h3>
<div>
  Create a customer
</div>
<b>Resource URL </b>
<div>
http://ragpickers.herokuapp.com/api/customers
</div>
<b>sample request</b>
<div>
  curl --data "customer[name]=bao&customer[phone_number]=01234567892&token=login_token" "http://ragpickers.herokuapp.com/api/ragpicker/customers"
</div>
<h4> Parameters</h4>
<table border="1" style="width:100%">
  <tr>
    <th style='width: 200px'> Name </th>
    <th style='width: 100px'>Required</th>
    <th style='width: 100px'>Data type</th>
    <th>Description</th>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>token</td>
    <td>Y</td>
    <td>string</td>
    <td>authentication token that api sign_in returned</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>customer[name]</td>
    <td>Y</td>
    <td>string</td>
    <td>Name</td>
  </tr>

  <tr>
    <td>customer[phone_number]</td>
    <td>Y</td>
    <td>string</td>
    <td>Phone number</td>
  </tr>
</table>

<h4>Response </h4>
<div>
 a json object
</div>
<h4>sample response</h4>
<table border="1" style="width:100%">
  <tr>
    <td>
      {"customer":{"id":1,"name":"bao","phone_number":"01234567892"}}
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
